overview: The user requested a "Surprise me" button to be added to the main
  posts display. This button, styled with the secondary variant, needed to be
  placed at the top right and, when clicked, navigate to a random post. The
  initial implementation used  from  for this
  purpose. However, this approach encountered a  due to missing
  imports, and subsequently, a persistent module factory error related to
  . Despite attempts to re-add the necessary imports and
  declarations, the  issue persisted. To resolve the navigation
  problem and ensure functionality, the implementation was modified to use
   for redirecting to a random post, effectively bypassing
  the  module resolution error.
